      • linearRange

        public static Cell2DDataset linearRange(ListNumber data,
                                        Range xRange,
                                        int xCount,
                                        Range yRange,
                                        int yCount)
        returns a Cell2DDataset, which is a 1D list of values that is treated like a 2D matrix.
        Parameters:
        data - 1D list of z-values. x and y coordinates are calculated by partitioning the matrix into pieces of length xCount. # of rows = yCount # of cols = xCount.
        xRange - the range of the x
        xCount - the number of x cells
        yRange - the range of the y
        yCount - the number of y cells
        Returns:
        the new dataset
